title: Teemoing icons
body: I still haven't gotten one icon for winning (teemoing and gauntlet on lvl 40smthing) and the one from mini game. Do I just have to wait more or is it a bug?

replies.body:
I haven't recieved one for senidng a gift
{{sticker:zombie-brand-clap}}

As *Zombiemaster* mentioned, the [Teemoing 2016 page](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/skins/the-teemoing-2016) mentions that November 17th is the final day to receive these icons. If you don't have one after the 17th passes by, hit us up in a [support ticket.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new)

Let me know if you have any questions.
I had the same question, Thank you for responding this topic. {{champion:17}}
Do we have to beat both the Teemoing and the Gauntlet to get the icon or is beating just the Teemoing fine?
Any *Doom bots* mode is fine, it doesn't have to be the gauntlet.
nah, you just need to beat the Teemoing in general

Thanks for the note on the date! I imagine the reason this question is popping up (I had it too) is that on the event page, it says you'll get the icon for beating Doombots "up to one week" after beating it. That made me assume that if I still didn't have it despite winning last weekend, I should ask someone.
Same here, yeah, I know I gotta wait till 17th but it{{sticker:zombie-nunu-bummed}}  hurts the eye when all your friends have unlocked it.....And they all be staring down on you in the Club Chat . XD
same!! I wait that for a weak now.
You just need to wait. The icons can take up to two weeks after November 3rd to be added to your account.
